			"width": 309.375,
			"height": 68.75,
			"text": "From Karpathy's LLM Wiki:\n· Three-layer architecture (raw → wiki → schema)\n· index.md + log.md as structural files\n· Ingest / Query / Lint operations\n· Index-over-RAG retrieval",
			"originalText": "From Karpathy's LLM Wiki:\n· Three-layer architecture (raw → wiki → schema)\n· index.md + log.md as structural files\n· Ingest / Query / Lint operations\n· Index-over-RAG retrieval",
